  "sentences": [
    {
      "text": "Two trillion dollars.",
      "start_ms": 50,
      "end_ms": 1681,
      "start_f": 1,
      "end_f": 50
    },
    {
      "text": "Zero proof.",
      "start_ms": 1681,
      "end_ms": 2931,
      "start_f": 50,
      "end_f": 87
    },
    {
      "text": "AI agents are executing transactions, managing DAO treasuries, making financial decisions — right now.",
      "start_ms": 2931,
      "end_ms": 10514,
      "start_f": 87,
      "end_f": 315
    },
    {
      "text": "And there is no mathematical proof any of them behaved correctly.",
      "start_ms": 10514,
      "end_ms": 14681,
      "start_f": 315,
      "end_f": 440
    },
    {
      "text": "You would not trust a bridge that was probably structurally sound.",
      "start_ms": 14681,
      "end_ms": 18417,
      "start_f": 440,
      "end_f": 552
    },
    {
      "text": "But every autonomous agent fleet runs on probably.",
      "start_ms": 18417,
      "end_ms": 21653,
      "start_f": 552,
      "end_f": 649
    },
    {
      "text": "Rules encoded as prompts can be overridden at any moment.",
      "start_ms": 21653,
      "end_ms": 25903,
      "start_f": 649,
      "end_f": 777
    },
    {
      "text": "Language models hallucinate.",
      "start_ms": 25903,
      "end_ms": 28014,
      "start_f": 777,
      "end_f": 840
    },
    {
      "text": "A validator that lies cannot validate.",
      "start_ms": 28014,
      "end_ms": 30833,
      "start_f": 840,
      "end_f": 925
    },
    {
      "text": "Audit logs can be altered after the fact.",
      "start_ms": 30833,
      "end_ms": 33639,
      "start_f": 925,
      "end_f": 1009
    },
    {
      "text": "The entire AI agent stack is built on trust — and trust is not a proof.",
      "start_ms": 33639,
      "end_ms": 39403,
      "start_f": 1009,
      "end_f": 1182
    },
    {
      "text": "DOF-MESH changes this.",
      "start_ms": 39403,
      "end_ms": 41389,
      "start_f": 1182,
      "end_f": 1241
    },
    {
      "text": "We are the first framework that mathematically proves an AI agent behaved correctly — before it acts.",
      "start_ms": 41389,
      "end_ms": 48056,
      "start_f": 1241,
      "end_f": 1441
    },
    {
      "text": "Three independent deterministic layers.",
      "start_ms": 48056,
      "end_ms": 50958,
      "start_f": 1441,
      "end_f": 1528
    },
    {
      "text": "Layer one: Constitution enforcement.",
      "start_ms": 50958,
      "end_ms": 53931,
      "start_f": 1528,
      "end_f": 1617
    },
    {
      "text": "Deterministic rules.",
      "start_ms": 53931,
      "end_ms": 55667,
      "start_f": 1617,
      "end_f": 1670
    },
    {
      "text": "Zero language models in the decision path.",
      "start_ms": 55667,
      "end_ms": 58653,
      "start_f": 1670,
      "end_f": 1759
    },
    {
      "text": "Layer two: Z3 SMT formal verification.",
      "start_ms": 58653,
      "end_ms": 63153,
      "start_f": 1759,
      "end_f": 1894
    },
    {
      "text": "Four theorems proven for all possible inputs — by Microsoft Research's solver.",
      "start_ms": 63153,
      "end_ms": 68986,
      "start_f": 1894,
      "end_f": 2069
    },
    {
      "text": "Layer three: TRACER score.",
      "start_ms": 68986,
      "end_ms": 71403,
      "start_f": 2069,
      "end_f": 2142
    },
    {
      "text": "Five-dimensional behavioral quality scoring.",
      "start_ms": 71403,
      "end_ms": 74292,
      "start_f": 2142,
      "end_f": 2228
    },
    {
      "text": "The result: a keccak256 proof hash, registered permanently on Conflux — tamper-proof forever.",
      "start_ms": 74292,
      "end_ms": 82597,
      "start_f": 2228,
      "end_f": 2477
    },
    {
      "text": "Why now?",
      "start_ms": 82597,
      "end_ms": 83528,
      "start_f": 2477,
      "end_f": 2505
    },
    {
      "text": "Three hundred twenty-seven million AI agents will be deployed by 2027.",
      "start_ms": 83528,
      "end_ms": 88944,
      "start_f": 2505,
      "end_f": 2668
    },
    {
      "text": "The AI governance market reaches forty-seven billion dollars by 2030.",
      "start_ms": 88944,
      "end_ms": 94264,
      "start_f": 2668,
      "end_f": 2827
    },
    {
      "text": "And today — zero frameworks offer formal mathematical proof.",
      "start_ms": 94264,
      "end_ms": 98778,
      "start_f": 2827,
      "end_f": 2963
    },
    {
      "text": "The infrastructure gap is open.",
      "start_ms": 98778,
      "end_ms": 101167,
      "start_f": 2963,
      "end_f": 3035
    },
    {
      "text": "We built the solution.",
      "start_ms": 101167,
      "end_ms": 102708,
      "start_f": 3035,
      "end_f": 3081
    },
    {
      "text": "Watch this live.",
      "start_ms": 102708,
      "end_ms": 103986,
      "start_f": 3081,
      "end_f": 3119
    },
    {
      "text": "Agent 1687 requests a DeFi transaction on Conflux eSpace.",
      "start_ms": 103986,
      "end_ms": 109986,
      "start_f": 3119,
      "end_f": 3299
    },
    {
      "text": "DOF-MESH intercepts it before execution.",
      "start_ms": 109986,
      "end_ms": 113278,
      "start_f": 3299,
      "end_f": 3398
    },
    {
      "text": "Constitution check: passed.",
      "start_ms": 113278,
      "end_ms": 115667,
      "start_f": 3398,
      "end_f": 3470
    },
    {
      "text": "Zero language models involved.",
      "start_ms": 115667,
      "end_ms": 117931,
      "start_f": 3470,
      "end_f": 3537
    },
    {
      "text": "Z3 formal verification: four of four theorems proven in seven milliseconds.",
      "start_ms": 117931,
      "end_ms": 124333,
      "start_f": 3537,
      "end_f": 3730
    },
    {
      "text": "TRACER behavioral score: zero point seven one two — well above threshold.",
      "start_ms": 124333,
      "end_ms": 130319,
      "start_f": 3730,
      "end_f": 3909
    },
    {
      "text": "The agent qualifies.",
      "start_ms": 130319,
      "end_ms": 132056,
      "start_f": 3909,
      "end_f": 3961
    },
    {
      "text": "Now it goes on-chain.",
      "start_ms": 132056,
      "end_ms": 133583,
      "start_f": 3961,
      "end_f": 4007
    },
    {
      "text": "Here is the proof.",
      "start_ms": 133583,
      "end_ms": 134903,
      "start_f": 4007,
      "end_f": 4047
    },
    {
      "text": "Permanent.",
      "start_ms": 134903,
      "end_ms": 135861,
      "start_f": 4047,
      "end_f": 4075
    },
    {
      "text": "One hundred forty-five confirmed transactions on DOFProofRegistryV1.",
      "start_ms": 135861,
      "end_ms": 141500,
      "start_f": 4075,
      "end_f": 4245
    },
    {
      "text": "And our latest innovation: V2 Proof-to-Gasless.",
      "start_ms": 141500,
      "end_ms": 145500,
      "start_f": 4245,
      "end_f": 4365
    },
    {
      "text": "When an agent proves mathematical compliance — TRACER above zero point four, Constitution above ninety percent — it is automatically added to Conflux's SponsorWhitelistControl.",
      "start_ms": 145500,
      "end_ms": 158111,
      "start_f": 4365,
      "end_f": 4743
    },
    {
      "text": "Its next transactions cost zero gas.",
      "start_ms": 158111,
      "end_ms": 161306,
      "start_f": 4743,
      "end_f": 4839
    },
    {
      "text": "Math earns economic privilege.",
      "start_ms": 161306,
      "end_ms": 163819,
      "start_f": 4839,
      "end_f": 4914
    },
    {
      "text": "That is new.",
      "start_ms": 163819,
      "end_ms": 164861,
      "start_f": 4914,
      "end_f": 4945
    },
    {
      "text": "Why Conflux?",
      "start_ms": 164861,
      "end_ms": 166208,
      "start_f": 4945,
      "end_f": 4986
    },
    {
      "text": "Because Gas Sponsorship is architecturally necessary for agent infrastructure.",
      "start_ms": 166208,
      "end_ms": 171625,
      "start_f": 4986,
      "end_f": 5148
    },
    {
      "text": "Agents should not hold gas — they should act.",
      "start_ms": 171625,
      "end_ms": 174667,
      "start_f": 5148,
      "end_f": 5240
    },
    {
      "text": "Conflux's native SponsorWhitelistControl makes zero-friction compliance registration possible at any scale.",
      "start_ms": 174667,
      "end_ms": 182417,
      "start_f": 5240,
      "end_f": 5472
    },
    {
      "text": "On Ethereum, every agent needs gas.",
      "start_ms": 182417,
      "end_ms": 185514,
      "start_f": 5472,
      "end_f": 5565
    },
    {
      "text": "On Conflux, math replaces money.",
      "start_ms": 185514,
      "end_ms": 188347,
      "start_f": 5565,
      "end_f": 5650
    },
    {
      "text": "No other EVM chain has this natively.",
      "start_ms": 188347,
      "end_ms": 191403,
      "start_f": 5650,
      "end_f": 5742
    },
    {
      "text": "Three revenue streams.",
      "start_ms": 191403,
      "end_ms": 193153,
      "start_f": 5742,
      "end_f": 5794
    },
    {
      "text": "First: the open-source SDK.",
      "start_ms": 193153,
      "end_ms": 195972,
      "start_f": 5794,
      "end_f": 5879
    },
    {
      "text": "Developers run pip install dof-sdk — Conflux integration ships included.",
      "start_ms": 195972,
      "end_ms": 202222,
      "start_f": 5879,
      "end_f": 6066
    },
    {
      "text": "Second: the compliance API at ninety-nine to nine hundred ninety-nine dollars per month.",
      "start_ms": 202222,
      "end_ms": 208222,
      "start_f": 6066,
      "end_f": 6246
    },
    {
      "text": "Finance.",
      "start_ms": 208222,
      "end_ms": 209306,
      "start_f": 6246,
      "end_f": 6279
    },
    {
      "text": "Healthcare.",
      "start_ms": 209306,
      "end_ms": 210292,
      "start_f": 6279,
      "end_f": 6308
    },
    {
      "text": "Legal.",
      "start_ms": 210292,
      "end_ms": 211125,
      "start_f": 6308,
      "end_f": 6333
    },
    {
      "text": "Any team that cannot afford an agent that lies.",
      "start_ms": 211125,
      "end_ms": 214375,
      "start_f": 6333,
      "end_f": 6431
    },
    {
      "text": "Third: enterprise white-label licensing.",
      "start_ms": 214375,
      "end_ms": 217597,
      "start_f": 6431,
      "end_f": 6527
    },
    {
      "text": "Fifty thousand to five hundred thousand dollars per year.",
      "start_ms": 217597,
      "end_ms": 221194,
      "start_f": 6527,
      "end_f": 6635
    },
    {
      "text": "DAO treasuries, DeFi protocols, full agent fleets.",
      "start_ms": 221194,
      "end_ms": 225569,
      "start_f": 6635,
      "end_f": 6767
    },
    {
      "text": "The total addressable market for AI governance reaches eighteen billion by 2028.",
      "start_ms": 225569,
      "end_ms": 231792,
      "start_f": 6767,
      "end_f": 6953
    },
    {
      "text": "Our serviceable market — blockchain AI agent compliance — is three point two billion.",
      "start_ms": 231792,
      "end_ms": 237903,
      "start_f": 6953,
      "end_f": 7137
    },
    {
      "text": "Our realistic capture in year three: one hundred sixty million, starting with DeFi protocols needing provably-correct agents.",
      "start_ms": 237903,
      "end_ms": 246889,
      "start_f": 7137,
      "end_f": 7406
    },
    {
      "text": "This is not a prototype.",
      "start_ms": 246889,
      "end_ms": 248500,
      "start_f": 7406,
      "end_f": 7455
    },
    {
      "text": "One hundred forty-seven on-chain attestations on Conflux alone.",
      "start_ms": 248500,
      "end_ms": 252903,
      "start_f": 7455,
      "end_f": 7587
    },
    {
      "text": "Eight active chains.",
      "start_ms": 252903,
      "end_ms": 254472,
      "start_f": 7587,
      "end_f": 7634
    },
    {
      "text": "Four thousand three hundred eight tests passing.",
      "start_ms": 254472,
      "end_ms": 257236,
      "start_f": 7634,
      "end_f": 7717
    },
    {
      "text": "Two hundred thirty-eight autonomous agent cycles completed.",
      "start_ms": 257236,
      "end_ms": 261028,
      "start_f": 7717,
      "end_f": 7830
    },
    {
      "text": "Six MCP tools fully operational — the first Model Context Protocol server for Conflux Network.",
      "start_ms": 261028,
      "end_ms": 268500,
      "start_f": 7830,
      "end_f": 8055
    },
    {
      "text": "ERC-8004, the Autonomous Agent Identity Standard, submitted to Ethereum Magicians.",
      "start_ms": 268500,
      "end_ms": 276847,
      "start_f": 8055,
      "end_f": 8305
    },
    {
      "text": "I am Juan Carlos Quiceno — solo builder from Medellín, Colombia.",
      "start_ms": 276847,
      "end_ms": 281889,
      "start_f": 8305,
      "end_f": 8456
    },
    {
      "text": "I built every line of this: the framework, the contracts, the MCP server, the SDK.",
      "start_ms": 281889,
      "end_ms": 289208,
      "start_f": 8456,
      "end_f": 8676
    },
    {
      "text": "My ask is simple: help us deploy to Conflux mainnet, connect us with regulated-industry partners, and recognize this as the missing infrastructure layer for AI on blockchain.",
      "start_ms": 289208,
      "end_ms": 301625,
      "start_f": 8676,
      "end_f": 9048
    },
    {
      "text": "The math is proven.",
      "start_ms": 301625,
      "end_ms": 303236,
      "start_f": 9048,
      "end_f": 9097
    },
    {
      "text": "The chain is ready.",
      "start_ms": 303236,
      "end_ms": 304583,
      "start_f": 9097,
      "end_f": 9137
    },
    {
      "text": "The agents are waiting.",
      "start_ms": 304583,
      "end_ms": 306069,
      "start_f": 9137,
      "end_f": 9182
    },
    {
      "text": "Most frameworks verify what happened.",
      "start_ms": 306218,
      "end_ms": 308612,
      "start_f": 9186,
      "end_f": 9258
    },
    {
      "text": "DOF verifies what is about to happen.",
      "start_ms": 308612,
      "end_ms": 311251,
      "start_f": 9258,
      "end_f": 9337
    }
  ]
}